game.name: Find My Pokemon Go
game.description:
Hey Pokemon lovers, here is something great for you. All you need to do is to become the part of an ultimate Pokemon adventurous journey. Here is a super fun memory challenge which you will have to sort out by playing the role of a super talented Pokemon trainer in this fee online puzzle game. You must try out this arcade game at least once in a lifetime if you are seriously a pokemon lover. Your cognitive and memory skills will be tested while exploring all the tasks of this cool sports game.  
Find My Pokemon Go is a brand new arcade game for boys and girls where you are definitely going to have fun. Tap to flip over the cards that you see on the screen and match two identical pokemon to earn some rewards in the form of points. A respected score will help you move to the advanced level. Remember that you will have to spot all the pairs of pokemon in the given time. The proper implementation of the mouse will trigger you to complete the goal on time. 
Pay attention to the details and you will surely do a great job in this cool arcade game. Turn the cards and see if you flip the cards with the same picture of pokemon. Cards will be disappeared from the screen once you will get the points. You will lose your game if you cannot succeed in spotting the pairs before the time runs out. Do your best and make a great job in this exclusively-designed mobile game!
